<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
	<meta charset="euc-kr">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>NICE지키미</title>

	<script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
	<script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/ui.common.js"></script>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../css/zkm/rzm/common.css">
	<script type="text/javascript">
		mbHeader = { title: '회원가입', prev: true, menu: true };
		$(document).ready(function () {
			$('#agreeAllChk1').uiCheckAll();
		});
	</script>
</head>

<body>
	<div id="wrap">
		<div id="skipNavi">
			<a href="#content">본문내용 바로가기</a>
		</div>
		<!-- header -->
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/header.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/breadcrumbs.js"></script>
		<!--// header -->

		<!-- container -->
		<div id="container">
			<div id="content">
				<div class="section">
					<div class="governing">
						<h2 class="governingTitle">약관에 동의해 주세요.</h2>
					</div>

					<div class="agreement" id="agreeAllChk1">
						<div class="agreeTitle">
							<input type="checkbox" id="agreeAll" data-chk-item="all"><label for="agreeAll"><span>전체 동의</span></label>
						</div>
						<div class="agreeSection">
							<ul class="agreeList">
								<li data-chk-item="list">
									<div class="uiItem">
										<input type="checkbox" id="agr01" data-chk-item="list-item"><label for="agr01">[필수] 나이스지키미 이용약관 동의</label>
									</div>
									<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">약관 상세보기</span></a>
								</li>
								<li data-chk-item="list">
									<div class="uiItem">
										<input type="checkbox" id="agr02" data-chk-item="list-item"><label for="agr02">[필수] 개인정보수집 및 제공 동의</label>
									</div>
									<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">약관 상세보기</span></a>
									<div class="agreeSub">
										<a href="#none" class="agrLink">개인정보처리방침 전체보기</a>
									</div>
								</li>
								<li data-chk-item="list">
									<div class="uiItem">
										<input type="checkbox" id="agr03" data-chk-item="list-item"><label for="agr03">[필수] 고유식별정보 처리 동의</label>
									</div>
									<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">약관 상세보기</span></a>
								</li>
							</ul>
							<div class="uiAcco">
								<div data-chk-item="list">
									<div class="uiAccoHeader">
										<div class="uiItem">
											<input type="checkbox" id="agr1" data-chk-item="list-item"><label for="agr1">[선택] 신용정보 변동 알람</label>
										</div>
										<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">펼치기</span></a>
									</div>
									<div class="uiAccoContent">
										<div class="subSelBox">
											<p>회원정보, 결제 등 서비스 이용 및 약관변동 소식은 신용정보 변동 알람과 별도로 메일 또는 SMS로 전송해 드려요.</p>
											<ul class="agreeItem">
												<li>
													<input type="checkbox" id="agr11" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="agr11">문자/알림톡</label>
												</li>
												<li>
													<input type="checkbox" id="agr12" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="agr12">이메일</label>
												</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div data-chk-item="list">
									<div class="uiAccoHeader">
										<div class="uiItem">
											<input type="checkbox" id="agr2" data-chk-item="list-item"><label for="agr2">[선택] 마케팅정보 활용동의</label>
										</div>
										<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">펼치기</span></a>
									</div>
									<div class="uiAccoContent">
										<div class="subSelBox">
											<p>제휴서비스, 마케팅, 이벤트상품 등 프로모션 정보에 대한 알람을 받을 수 있어요.</p>
											<div class="agreeSub"><a href="#none" class="agrLink">마케팅정보 활용동의 (선택)</a></div>
											<ul class="agreeItem">
												<li>
													<input type="checkbox" id="agr21" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="agr21">문자/알림톡</label>
												</li>
												<li>
													<input type="checkbox" id="agr22" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="agr22">이메일</label>
												</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
									</div>

								</div>
								<div data-chk-item="list">
									<div class="uiAccoHeader">
										<div class="uiItem">
											<input type="checkbox" id="agr3" data-chk-item="list-item"><label for="agr3">[선택] 맞춤정보 수신 동의</label>
										</div>
										<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">펼치기</span></a>
									</div>
									<div class="uiAccoContent">
										<ul class="agreeItem">
											<li>
												<input type="checkbox" id="agr31" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="agr31">개인(신용)정보 수집 이용동의(맞춤형 정보 수신) (선택)</label>
												<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">약관 상세보기</span></a>
											</li>
											<li>
												<input type="checkbox" id="agr32" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="agr32">개인(신용)정보 제공동의(맞춤형 정보 수신) (선택)</label>
												<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">약관 상세보기</span></a>
											</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
								</div>

							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bottomActBtns">
						<div class="btns">
							<button type="button" class="btn primary"><span>다음</span></button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--// container -->

		<!-- footer -->
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/footer.js"></script>
		<!--// footer -->
	</div>
</body>

</html>